{"tid":1997804,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本自駕路線分享(行程指南/自駕心得)","createTime":"2020-05-02T02:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T08:17:27.000Z","uid":110125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62b49debed35b55fe7fea76c1d23717da0b68918","tid":1997804,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"呢排大家都冇得去旅行,日日番工望住啲旅行相,睇都睇到流哂口水.<br />\n突然心血來潮想同大家分享下我自駕去過嘅地方.<br />\n因為自駕嘅時侯大家都唔知實際路況/腳程係點<br />\n可能都唔會plan太多地方<br />\n同埋始終睇vlog都唔會太提及自駕要留意嘅野<br />\n希望呢個post可以同大家交流下自駕去過嘅行程/要留意嘅野<br />\n<br />\n小弟去過熊本(夏)/四國(春)/群馬(秋)/東北(冬) 自駕<br />\n今次想先分享東北行程先<br />\n由於我係係東京降落然後搭JR去仙台<br />\n所以第一日係唔會租車,行程開始會變左係day2<br />\n(因為我去親都係早機/凌晨機,第一日租車怕出事)<br />\n先po個大約線路先,()入面係上一個地方去目的地嘅時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLNdPUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLNdPUR.jpg&h=9fc20a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDAY2:仙台拎車-宮城藏王狐狸村(1.2hr)-山形市內(1.4hr)-山形銀山溫泉(1hr)-住山形市內<br />\nDAY3-山形市內-藏王山/纜車樹冰/滑雪(唔識)/溫泉/(45min)-霞城公園(45min)-住山形市內<br />\nDAY4-山形市內-大內宿(2.3hr/有雪地)-湯野上溫泉站(15min)-會津若松市內(1.7hr)-住會津若松市內<br />\nDAY5-會津若松市內-鶴ヶ城天守-只見線第一鐵橋(1.5hr)-豬苗代湖(1.8hr)-福島市內(1.3hr)-住福島市內<br />\nDAY6-福島市內-仙台還車(1.2hr)-仙台JR青森-青森市內-住青森市內<br />\nDAY2-DAY-6 791KM<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5Jc5ui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5Jc5ui.jpg&h=286228bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDAY7-青森拎車-八甲田山(45min)-奧入瀨溪流(路過)-十和田湖雪祭(1.2hr)-住青森市內(1.5hr)<br />\nDAY8-青森還車-弘前城-青森JR東京 <br />\n<br />\n今次租左兩架車,都係係times租車.<br />\n一架係prius 1.8 e-four. 1架係imperza 1.6 <br />\n冬天租車一般都會送雪tire,但4驅就要加錢(好似係)<br />\n本身我諗住撞下會唔會唔加錢有4驅,點知真係送埋比我(E-four)<br />\n滿心歡喜咁渣,就咁渣落去同普通ff冇乜分別<br />\n直到我去到福島縣道329,果時嘅雪量大約係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JD8DYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JD8DYz.jpg&h=5484b72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行緊40,係入彎前係咁2踩下個brake<br />\n成架車轟轟轟咁向前冼出去<br />\n果斷鬆腳等個騼grip番地下之後先扭駄<br />\n所以大家渣雪地記得brake test,唔好入彎前先黎收,直路好收定先<br />\n更加唔好大腳踢死佢,feel到唔對路就唔好再踩<br />\n吊住個brake用正常速度扭駄博佢ball out算<br />\n踩死左打白鴿轉就係咁先<br />\n之後去青森渣imperza,租之前已經問定呢架野4驅係咪要加錢<br />\n佢話係,心諗渣得subaru冇4驅咁渣黎做乜,當佢吹水應該有嘅<br />\n結果真係有4驅,唔洗加錢<br />\n上到八甲田山D雪地簡地如履平地,踩深brake會有冼嘅感覺<br />\n但好快就正常番,所以自問雪地冇信心嘅人可以租imperza<br />\n<br />\nprius油耗大約22km/L(eco mode)<br />\nImperza1.6就 15km/L(normal)<br />\n正常渣,有時踩兩腳咁樣 <br />\n<br />\n轉頭會係咁2 po下D唔靚ge景點相<br />\n自駕嘅好處就係可以想去邊就去邊,可以訓晏D唔洗趕車(每日930出門)<br />\n沿路見到靚嘅風景就可以停埋一邊影相<br />\n唔好處就係全程如果得一個司機 連續行D比較長嘅隧道會恰眼訓<br />\n如果大家有好嘅日本自駕路線都可以係到分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a7b1cb45bcec0281dc7df39356295273c3a64","tid":1997804,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:55:18.000Z","msg":"十和田湖雪祭。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESg2Jzt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESg2Jzt.jpg&h=cc2740e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八甲田山。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0KLGmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0KLGmc.jpg&h=7812758d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青森港。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VskrqRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVskrqRL.jpg&h=49da5779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n弘前城。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8RaSwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8RaSwH.jpg&h=02271fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十和田湖。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYD8EbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYD8EbK.jpg&h=43dace43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城倉大橋。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9tc5QB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9tc5QB.jpg&h=d02fa6a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睡魔博物館。青森<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boW2JDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FboW2JDr.jpg&h=cdf8e2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n猪苗代湖。福島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsZWN1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsZWN1e.jpg&h=cadcd783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只見線第一鐵橋。福島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZfyQeB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZfyQeB.jpg&h=d347ba9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大內宿。福島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1HNaeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1HNaeD.jpg&h=07828538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大內宿。褔島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4GuozF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4GuozF.jpg&h=b1a52f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鶴城。褔島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJvOEbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJvOEbO.jpg&h=532c2ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n霞城公園。山形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bOXxwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bOXxwP.jpg&h=51fab9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藏王山。山形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQRRBUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQRRBUH.jpg&h=3eefb3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Qa7aiv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Qa7aiv.jpg&h=a10741b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀山溫泉。山形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m37xmmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm37xmmp.jpg&h=d51fded5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藏王狐狸村。宮城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPRmZeF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPRmZeF.jpg&h=7ddc572f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBnpWYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBnpWYw.jpg&h=9f83f8a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56e2284248c45681d293dda1ae445ce1634a16e6","tid":1997804,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"本身四月第一次自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家無得去，所以未試過。通常有咩要注意"},{"pid":"d6ffbbae9aa5da2cf9f9eda3d6921d106f533fd9","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5017331844826685551f953d1f0eb00d44f0d918","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ffbbae9aa5da2cf9f9eda3d6921d106f533fd9","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fda195c6d292078cb41b62c3f20f874d05f6309","tid":1997804,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"其實除左掃把佬外都唔使對其他既所謂四驅咁興奮"},{"pid":"2a13b8a1d9c5fa69c7eb59f160d4313b978e99df","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5017331844826685551f953d1f0eb00d44f0d918","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ffbbae9aa5da2cf9f9eda3d6921d106f533fd9","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKpPoNj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKpPoNj.png&h=ac38e403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8bc97f4cdb4bcde29b82528dd781f13650d4d92","tid":1997804,"uid":9323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"我都玩過廣島一日來回角島大橋同元乃隅稻成神社<br />\n個日租咗部mx5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZpvSJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZpvSJF.jpg&h=85d048ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smTTQvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmTTQvq.jpg&h=c8e09194&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3arq4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3arq4u.jpg&h=d4852dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mq3AjoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmq3AjoR.jpg&h=2f96e207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後還車個陣<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4ai1Cv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4ai1Cv.png&h=098339e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f47d1d62b40058ca723850e55ca73f3d3663890","tid":1997804,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56e2284248c45681d293dda1ae445ce1634a16e6","tid":1997804,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"本身四月第一次自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家無得去，所以未試過。通常有咩要注意"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"1.保險 建議買最貴包埋noc果隻 萬一炒9左都可以拍下羅友走人<br />\n<br />\n2.highway pass 識得plan可以幫你慳好多錢<br />\n<br />\n3.泊車 好多景點都有附近露天場，大約150yen一個中 亦都有免費市營軴車場 可以搵定先去<br />\n<br />\n4.cut線 日本人好禮讓 基本上三線公路 類似彌敦道果種 左線係直去/轉左 中線直去 右線直去然後會分叉一個袋口淨係轉右 所以右線通常都會塞 中線最順 左線小塞 無咩必要可以行左/中線<br />\n<br />\n5.唔好行錯highway 有時gps會好fake，唔肯定寧願唔上，上左有機會渣三四個字先落得番黎<br />\n<br />\n6. highway一般行80 未見過有快相 跟住前車就可以了 有人帶頭先好衝 俾警察閃你就低埋一邊講英文 佢就會放你走"},{"pid":"dc438416d621cf25faf6974f21a1cac36e9141d9","tid":1997804,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fda195c6d292078cb41b62c3f20f874d05f6309","tid":1997804,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim